Package: inschooldata
Title: Fetch and Process Indiana School Data
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R:
    person("Al", "Martin", , "almartin@example.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Downloads and processes school data from the Indiana Department of
    Education (IDOE). Provides functions for fetching enrollment data from
    IDOE's Data Center and transforming it into tidy format for analysis.
    Supports historical data from 2006 to present across corporation (district)
    and school levels.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
RoxygenNote: 7.3.3
